PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Transport of certain persons as directors of the board of directors of the Halifax Port Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years. (Robert A. Wilson, Bedford, Nova Scotia, in the place of Lois Anne Glibbery, whose term has expired; Edward D. Kirby, Lower Sackville, Nova Scotia, in the place of Ernest A. Coates, whose term has expired; and Linda Marie Brennan, Dartmouth, Nova Scotia, in the place of Harald A. Norve, whose term has expired)
